# Workspace Context — ChickenPlinkoV2

## This Project

**ChickenPlinkoV2** is the **web reference/demo** of Chicken Plinko — a hyper-casual 2D Plinko game.
- Stack: Three.js (rendering) + Matter.js (physics) + Vite 6 + vanilla JS
- Deployed to GitHub Pages
- Game design doc: `GameDesignDoc.md`

## Relationship to MHE Project

This web version is being **ported to Meta Horizon Engine (MHE)**. The MHE project lives in a separate workspace:
- Path: `C:\Users\Brand\Documents\MetaProjects\CC_Dev_ChickenPlinko\`
- The MHE port uses DrawingSurface (2D), custom physics (no Matter.js), and XAML UI
- Changes here may inform MHE implementation but this is **not the production target**

## Shared Documentation

The MetaProjects workspace contains shared MHE docs:
- `C:\Users\Brand\Documents\MetaProjects\Documentation\Best Practices.md`
- `C:\Users\Brand\Documents\MetaProjects\Documentation\API Reference\` (Worlds SDK 0.0.9)

## Architecture Quick Reference

- Entry: `src/main.js` — bootstrap + animation loop
- Config: `src/config/constants.js` — all tunable values + VERSION
- Core: `src/core/` — Renderer, Physics, Camera, InputManager, AudioManager, AssetLoader
- Entities: `src/entities/` — Chicken, Egg, Peg, Bin, AutoChicken
- Systems: `src/systems/` — GameLoop (state machine), Board, ParticleSystem, ScoreManager, Environment, Settings
- UI: `src/ui/HUD.js` — DOM overlay for gold, upgrades, settings
